com.redhat.rhn.testing

Class ForwardWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.struts.config.BaseConfig
      • org.apache.struts.config.ForwardConfig
        • org.apache.struts.action.ActionForward
          • com.redhat.rhn.testing.ForwardWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ForwardWrapper
extends org.apache.struts.action.ActionForward
    A decorator for a ActionForward. In addition to decorating a forward, this class adds the capability of getting parameters from the forward's path with getParam(java.lang.String) and getLongParam(java.lang.String).
